 href=\"/recruit/integration_inform/\" class=\"u-hover\">デジタル・システムコース 積極採用中！</a>\r\n          </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <div class=\"l-global_sp__sns\">\r\n          <a href=\"https://instagram.com/82group_recruit\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"u-hover\">採用公式アカウント</a>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <ul class=\"l-global_sp__bottom__02\">\r\n          <li>\r\n            <a href=\"https://bank.82group.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">八十二長野銀行公式サイトへ</a>\r\n          </li>\r\n          <li>\r\n            <a href=\"https://bank.82group.jp/privacy/\" target=\"_blank\">個人情報の保護について</a>\r\n          </li>\r\n          <li>\r\n            <a href=\"https://bank.82group.jp/use.html\" target=\"_blank\">サイトのご利用にあたって</a>\r\n          </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"l-global_sp__footer\">\r\n        <a href=\"/recruit/entry_bunrui.html\" class=\"l-global_sp__footer__entry\">\r\n          <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/entry_btn.svg\" alt=\"ENTRY\">\r\n        </a>\r\n        <a href=\"/recruit/\" class=\"l-global_sp__footer__gotop\">\r\n          TOPへ\r\n        </a>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <!-- // sp global nav -->\r\n\r\n  <div class=\"j-kv\">\r\n    <h1 class=\"u-fadein_02\">\r\n      <span class=\"j-kv__heading_01\">\r\n        <div class=\"u-ttlani\">\r\n          <span>W</span><span>o</span><span>r</span><span>k</span><span>s</span>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </span>\r\n      <span class=\"j-kv__heading_02\">業務紹介＆MOVIE</span>\r\n    </h1>\r\n    <p class=\"u-fadein_02\">法人・個人問わず、地域のお客さまのあらゆる課題に向き合い、<br class=\"u-pc__inline\">さまざまなソリューションを提供しています。</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <ul class=\"j-menu u-fadein\">\r\n    <li>\r\n      <a href=\"#Workflow\" class=\"u-hover\">業務体制</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n      <a href=\"#Job\" class=\"u-hover\">業務内容・各担当のミッション</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n\r\n  <div id=\"Workflow\" class=\"j-workflow\">\r\n    <h2 class=\"j-workflow__heading_h2 u-fadein\">\r\n      <p class=\"j-workflow__heading_h2_01\">Workflow</p>\r\n      <span class=\"j-workflow__heading_h2_02\">業務体制</span>\r\n    </h2>\r\n    <div class=\"j-workflow__flow u-fadein\">\r\n      <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/flow_img.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <div id=\"Job\" class=\"j-job\">\r\n    <h2 class=\"j-job__heading_h2 u-fadein\">\r\n      <p class=\"j-job__heading_h2_01\">Job &amp; Mission</p>\r\n      <span class=\"j-job__heading_h2_02\">業務内容・各担当のミッション</span>\r\n    </h2>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"j-job__bg -bg_j-job__bg_left u-fadein\">\r\n      <div class=\"j-job__cnt -bg_j-job__cnt_left\">\r\n        <div class=\"j-job__cnt__ttl u-fadein\">\r\n          <h3 class=\"j-job__heading_h3\"><span>支店</span></h3>\r\n          <p class=\"j-job__cnt__ttl__txt\">担当エリア、地域のお客さまの窓口として課題解決を行う</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec u-fadein\">\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__ico\">\r\n            <h4 class=\"j-job__heading_h4\">\r\n              <span class=\"j-job__ico01\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ico_01.svg\" alt=\"\"></span>法人営業\r\n            </h4>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt\">\r\n            <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_01\">お客さまの経営課題に向き合い、<br class=\"u-pc__inline\">地域の未来に貢献する</p>\r\n            <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_02 u-justify\">担当エリアのお取引先に対し、融資相談、提案を行います。また、販路開拓や新規事業支援などお客さまの経営課題に対するコンサルティング業務や、経営改善に向けたサポートも重要な役割です。</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__container\">\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person --height2\">\r\n              <a href=\"/recruit/works/people/03/\" class=\"u-hover\">\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__img\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_03.jpg\" alt=\"大和 昭広\" class=\"u-pc\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_03_sp.jpg\" alt=\"大和 昭広\" class=\"u-sp\">\r\n                </p>\r\n                <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt\">\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_01\">大和 昭広</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_02\">北信地区支店 ※取材当時<br>2007年入行<br>第一文学部卒</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person --height2\">\r\n              <a href=\"/recruit/works/people/04/\" class=\"u-hover\">\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__img\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_04.jpg\" alt=\"児玉 諒\" class=\"u-pc\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_04_sp.jpg\" alt=\"児玉 諒\" class=\"u-sp\">\r\n                </p>\r\n                <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt\">\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_01\">児玉 諒</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_02\">北信地区支店<br>2012年入行<br>地域行政学科卒</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec u-fadein\">\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__ico\">\r\n            <h4 class=\"j-job__heading_h4\">\r\n              <span class=\"j-job__ico02\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ico_02.svg\" alt=\"\"></span>個人営業\r\n            </h4>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt\">\r\n            <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_01\">お客さまの悩みを<br class=\"u-pc__inline\">金融・非金融両面から解決する</p>\r\n            <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_02 u-justify\">担当エリアの個人のお客さま向けに、資産運用・信託などのマネーアドバイザー業務や、住宅ローン等の個人のお客さま向けローンを提案します。また、日常のお困りごとを解決するライフサポートサービスも行っています。</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__container\">\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person --height2\">\r\n              <a href=\"/recruit/works/people/01/\" class=\"u-hover\">\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__img\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_01.jpg\" alt=\"北島 千鶴\" class=\"u-pc\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_01_sp.jpg\" alt=\"北島 千鶴\" class=\"u-sp\">\r\n                </p>\r\n                <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt\">\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_01\">北島 千鶴</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_02\">北信地区支店 ※取材当時<br>2004年入行<br>文学部卒</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person --height2\">\r\n              <a href=\"/recruit/works/people/02/\" class=\"u-hover\">\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__img\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_02.jpg\" alt=\"古畑 里紗\" class=\"u-pc\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_02_sp.jpg\" alt=\"古畑 里紗\" class=\"u-sp\">\r\n                </p>\r\n                <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt\">\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_01\">古畑 里紗</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_02\">南信地区支店<br>2018年入行<br>文学部卒</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"j-job__cnt__movie u-fadein\">\r\n          <h3>支店業務を動画でCheck！</h3>\r\n          <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn u-hover\" onclick=\"openMovie('6ivHyPt1O3o'); return false;\">\r\n            <h4 class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn__heading\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_btn_movie.svg\" alt=\"Special Movie\"></h4>\r\n            <p class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__txt\">Life at HNBK</p>\r\n          </a>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"j-job__bg -bg_j-job__bg_right u-fadein\">\r\n      <div class=\"j-job__cnt -bg_j-job__cnt_right\">\r\n        <div class=\"j-job__cnt__ttl u-fadein\">\r\n          <h3 class=\"j-job__heading_h3\"><span>本部</span></h3>\r\n          <p class=\"j-job__cnt__ttl__txt\">支店と連携し、専門的なスキル・知識を活かした支援、<br class=\"u-pc__inline\">商品の企画や銀行業務の改革がミッション</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__container --people06 u-fadein\">\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec\">\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__ico\">\r\n              <h4 class=\"j-job__heading_h4\">\r\n                <span class=\"j-job__ico03\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ico_03.svg\" alt=\"\"></span>支店<br>サポート\r\n              </h4>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt\">\r\n              <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_01\">ビジネスマッチング、M&A、事業承継など、<br class=\"u-pc__inline\">高度な支援を行う</p>\r\n              <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_02 u-justify\">お客さまの課題が高度化する中、支店だけでは解決することが難しいビジネスマッチングやM&A、事業承継、経営コンサルティングなどの高度な支援を行います。</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person\">\r\n              <a href=\"/recruit/works/people/06/\" class=\"u-hover\">\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__img\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_06.jpg\" alt=\"佐藤 駿\" class=\"u-pc\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_06_sp.jpg\" alt=\"佐藤 駿\" class=\"u-sp\">\r\n                </p>\r\n                <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt\">\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_01\">佐藤 駿</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_02\">営業渉外部<br>2013年入行<br>総合情報学部卒</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__movie u-fadein\">\r\n            <h3>支店サポート業務を動画でCheck！</h3>\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn__container\">\r\n              <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn u-hover\" onclick=\"openMovie('uT9WU43AC84'); return false;\">\r\n                <h4 class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn__heading\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_btn_movie.svg\" alt=\"Special Movie\"></h4>\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__txt\">事業承継・M&A</p>\r\n              </a>\r\n              <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn --structure u-hover\" onclick=\"openMovie('113MuTiJ_p4'); return false;\">\r\n                <h4 class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn__heading\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_btn_movie.svg\" alt=\"Special Movie\"></h4>\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__txt\">ストラクチャード<br>ファイナンス</p>\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__container --people05 u-fadein\">\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec\">\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__ico\">\r\n              <h4 class=\"j-job__heading_h4\">\r\n                <span class=\"j-job__ico04\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ico_04.svg\" alt=\"\"></span>商品企画\r\n              </h4>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt\">\r\n              <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_01\">信州の未来にどう貢献するか、<br class=\"u-pc__inline\">未来の八十二長野銀行の戦略を描く</p>\r\n              <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_02 u-justify\">八十二長野銀行の経営戦略・営業戦略の立案をはじめ、新商品や新規事業の開発などの企画業務を行います。信州の未来をどう変えていくか、八十二長野銀行と地域の未来を描く仕事です。</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person\">\r\n              <a href=\"/recruit/works/people/05/\" class=\"u-hover\">\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__img\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_05.jpg\" alt=\"林 暁彦\" class=\"u-pc\">\r\n                  <img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ph_05_sp.jpg\" alt=\"林 暁彦\" class=\"u-sp\">\r\n                </p>\r\n                <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt\">\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_01\">林 暁彦</p>\r\n                  <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__person__txt_02\">営業企画部<br>商品開発推進グループ<br>2010年入行<br>生産工学部卒</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__movie u-fadein\">\r\n            <h3>商品企画業務を動画でCheck！</h3>\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn__container\">\r\n              <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn u-hover\" onclick=\"openMovie('9V8MRT2Mq7E'); return false;\">\r\n                <h4 class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn__heading\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_btn_movie.svg\" alt=\"Special Movie\"></h4>\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__txt\">地域貢献</p>\r\n              </a>\r\n              <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn u-hover\" onclick=\"openMovie('Lmf0qj1_yLw'); return false;\">\r\n                <h4 class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__btn__heading\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_btn_movie.svg\" alt=\"Special Movie\"></h4>\r\n                <p class=\"j-job__cnt__movie__txt\">海外戦略</p>\r\n              </a>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__container --people08 u-fadein\">\r\n          <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec\">\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__ico\">\r\n              <h4 class=\"j-job__heading_h4\">\r\n                <span class=\"j-job__ico05\"><img src=\"/recruit/assets/images/works/jobs/jobs_ico_05.svg\" alt=\"\"></span>システム\r\n              </h4>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt\">\r\n              <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_01\">DX、FinTechなどの最新テクノロジーで<br class=\"u-pc__inline\">お客さまを支援する</p>\r\n              <p class=\"j-job__cnt__sec__txt_02 u-justify\">銀行システムの開発、運用をはじめ、